                        <zone id='15'>
                          <formatted-text>
                            <run fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>This dashboard presents the German labour market outlook for 2024–2030. Key indicators are shown at the top — including net job change, total structural change, and average automation risk. The treemap below reveals which industries are experiencing the most disruption, while the bar chart shows automation risk by sector. Recommendations and policy actions can be found on the right.</run>
