            <zone fixed-size='77' forceUpdate='true' h='10718' id='15' is-fixed='true' type-v2='text' w='98814' x='593' y='9503'>
              <formatted-text>
                <run fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>This dashboard presents the German labour market outlook for 2024–2030. Key indicators are shown at the top — including net job change, total structural change, and average automation risk. The treemap below reveals which industries are experiencing the most disruption, while the bar chart shows automation risk by sector. Recommendations and policy actions can be found on the right.&quot;</run>
              </formatted-text>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#5da3b2' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='solid' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='4' />
                <_.fcp.DashboardRoundedCorners.true...format attr='corner-radius' value='20' />
                <format attr='margin' value='10' />
                <format attr='padding' value='10' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
            <zone fixed-size='77' h='10718' id='3' is-fixed='true' name='German Policymaker - KPIs' show-title='false' w='98814' x='593' y='20221'>
              <layout-cache type-h='cell' type-w='fixed' />
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <format attr='margin' value='10' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
            <zone h='68177' id='8' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98814' x='593' y='30939'>
              <zone fixed-size='889' h='68177' id='6' is-fixed='true' type-v2='layout-basic' w='65852' x='593' y='30939'>
                <zone h='35352' id='5' name='Ger Policymaker - Treemap' w='65852' x='593' y='38213'>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='20' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
                <zone h='25551' id='10' name='Ger Policymaker - Automation Risk' w='65852' x='593' y='73565'>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='20' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
                <zone h='7274' id='9' name='Ger Policymaker - Treemap' pane-specification-id='0' param='[federated.0zkye0v0ev2j971b2q8he0505eqy].[usr:Calculation_4991624308985856:qk]' type-v2='color' w='65852' x='593' y='30939'>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='20' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
              </zone>
              <zone forceUpdate='true' h='68177' id='11' type-v2='text' w='32962' x='66445' y='30939'>
                <formatted-text>
                  <run bold='true' fontsize='11'>Policy Outlook</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontsize='11'>Germany&apos;s labour market appears stable with a net job change of just -0.21% by 2030. However, 65% of all current positions are in structural flux — millions of workers will need to transition between roles. With an average automation risk of 50%, proactive policy intervention is urgent.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true' fontsize='11'>Structural Change by Industry</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontsize='11'>The scale of workforce disruption is remarkably consistent across all industries — no sector is spared. However, net job gains and losses vary significantly. </run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true' fontsize='11'>Automation Risk by Industry</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontsize='11'>Automation risk is uniformly high across all industries, varying by no more than 2 percentage points around the 50% average. This confirms that automation is not an industry-specific challenge — it is a systemic one. Broad national reskilling initiatives are needed rather than sector-targeted responses.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>Key actions:</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>Reskilling programmes</run>
                  <run fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'> — With average automation risk at 50% across all industries, proactive retraining is urgent. No sector is immune.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>Finance sector priority</run>
                  <run fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'> — </run>
                  <run fontsize='11'>The financial sector faces the largest net job losses and should be the primary focus of cross-sector retraining and redeployment programmes.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>Structural not cyclical</run>
                  <run fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'> — This is not a recession. Jobs are not disappearing overall — they are shifting. Policy response should focus on workforce transition, not unemployment benefits.</run>
                </formatted-text>
                <zone-style>
                  <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                  <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                  <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                  <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                </zone-style>
              </zone>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
      </zones>
